  "description": "Set directly on the front line of the iconic Los Naranjos Golf Course, Villa Soñada is a character-filled 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom villa in the heart of Nueva Andalucía. Full of Spanish charm, this home blends traditional Andalusian architecture with laid-back outdoor living, offering panoramic views of the fairways and La Concha mountain from a peaceful, sun-soaked setting.\n\nInside, the villa features classic design elements like arched doorways, terracotta finishes, and textured walls, all complemented by tasteful modern updates. The open-plan living area connects to a fully equipped kitchen and casual dining space, creating a warm and welcoming flow for relaxing or entertaining. Each of the four bedrooms is bright and spacious, with three well-appointed bathrooms that combine rustic touches with comfort.\n\nOutside, guests can unwind by the private swimming pool, soak up the sun on the terrace, or enjoy long evenings overlooking the golf course. The garden offers space to relax in privacy, while the open views deliver a true Costa del Sol experience.\n\nLocated just minutes from Puerto Banús, Villa Soñada is ideally positioned near some of the coast’s best restaurants, bars, beach clubs, and boutique shopping. Whether you’re here to golf, dine, or simply unwind, this villa offers the perfect base for an unforgettable Marbella getaway.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
